# Title: Recon Activity via SASec
# Author: Sagie Dulce, Dekel Paz
# Date: 2022-01-01
# Level: high
# Description: Detects remote RPC calls to read information about scheduled tasks via SASec
# MITRE Tactic: Discovery
# Tags: attack.discovery
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/application/rpc_firewall/rpc_firewall_sasec_recon.yml

EventID=3 EventLog="RPCFW" InterfaceUuid="378e52b0-c0a9-11cf-822d-00aa0051e40f" NOT (OpNum IN (0, 1))